title: Smokey Chicken & Red Wine Jus with Kūmara Mash & Lemony Greens
description: Smokey, saucy, and seriously satisfying! Tender chicken strips are served over creamy kūmara mash with a side of zesty lemony greens and a generous pour of red wine jus—it’s a cosy-meets-classy combo that hits all the right notes.
This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.
